  "notes": "Similar to the [url=https://www.discogs.com/release/23949476-Beyoncé-Renaissance]Alternate Cover[/url] release, this original first pressing contains the interpolation of \"Milkshake\" by Kelis on track B2 \"Energy\", as well as the original offending lyric on track C4 \"Heated\", which were later changed on downloadable and streaming versions of the album, followed by [url=https://www.discogs.com/release/26411657-Beyoncé-Renaissance]new pressings[/url] of the album on [url=https://www.discogs.com/release/26478590-Beyoncé-Renaissance]Vinyl[/url] and CD. The runout markings on the discs help distinguish the original pressing from the later repressed versions.\n\n\nCollector's Edition housed in premium hard slipcase package\n2 printed jackets + 2 printed inner sleeves\n36-page photo booklet with lyrics and album credits\nIncludes 1 of 3 randomized 24\" x 36\" collectible double-sided posters\nDouble 180-gram vinyl set",
  "released_formatted": "07 Oct 2022",
